Direct Known Subclasses:
GovernanceControlProperties, GovernanceDriverProperties, GovernancePolicyProperties, GovernanceStrategyProperties, RegulationProperties
public class GovernanceDefinitionProperties extends AuthoredReferenceableProperties
GovernanceDefinitionProperties provides the base class for many of the definitions that define the data strategy and governance program.
